Buy Beaujolais Wines

   See all Winemakers in Beaujolais

   The Gamet is the flagship grape variety in the Beaujolais wine region,
   which stretches 55 kilometres long and about 15 kilometres wide. Some
   winemakers have also started producing Syrah and Viognier following the
   climate change of the region! The Beaujolais region is home to several
   famous winemakers (including Descombes, Coquelet, Lapalu, Joubert and
   Vionnet).
   En savoir plus
